# DB and API Schemas

- When implementing new API endpoint, always define the API schema first and setup the correct swagger to test the API!
- When adding a new data to database, define the database schema first and the appropriate migration file. 
- DB and API schemas should be defined under the `src/schemas/` directory
- DB schema should go into `src/schemas/db/`
- API schema should be defined under the `src/schemas/api/`